s feedback. our site - www.theshowvr.com\n\nOur Current Minigames:\n\n- **Green Light, Red Light**: Test your reflexes and strategy in this classic stop-and-go game.\n\n- **Snowball Fight**: Engage in epic snowball battles with realistic physics for an immersive experience.\n\n- **Falling Stones**: Dodge the falling obstacles and be the last one standing.\n\n- **Sky Fall**: Navigate through the skies and avoid obstacles in this aerial challenge.\n\n- **Green Mountain Obstacle Course**: Race against others in a thrilling obstacle course set on a treacherous green mountain.\n\n- **Bomb Tag**: Pass the bomb to other players to avoid getting blown up in this fast-paced game of tag.\n\n- **Stepping Glass**: Carefully step on the correct glass tiles without falling through in this nerve-wracking challenge.\n\n- **The Wall**: Are you ready to climb? Be the first to reach the top!\n\n**Minimum 2 players are required to start a match, please give us any feedback on discord & our site at www.theshowvr.com**\n\nOur goal is to make the funniest community multiplayer minigames game on VR :)\n\nThank you for trying out the game at an early stage!", "short_description": "Welcome to The Show VR, a unique multiplayer game that brings you and up to 15 other players into a world of fun minigames! Inspired by the best minigames in shows/games!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.theshowvr.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Kissi Studio", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.theshowvr.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1700921480735423"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommen